trans-unit.source: Represents an element of an X.509 chain.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et element av en X.509-kjede.

trans-unit.source: This object is constructed internally and is returned as part of an <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection> when calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.ChainElements%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Dette objektet bygges internt og returneres som en del av en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection>Når du kaller den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.ChainElements%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.ChainElements%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the X.509 certificate at a particular chain element.
trans-unit.target: Henter X.509-sertifikatet i en bestemt kjede-element.

trans-unit.source: This property returns an X.509 certificate for this element.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer et X.509-sertifikat for dette elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the error status of the current X.509 certificate in a chain.
trans-unit.target: Henter feilstatus sertifikatets gjeldende X.509 i en kjede.

trans-unit.source: This property returns an array of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainStatus> objects, each consisting of an error code bit and a descriptive localized error message.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer en matrise av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainStatus>objekter hver består av en feil code-biters og beskrivende oversatte feilmeldingen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainStatus>

trans-unit.source: Gets additional error information from an unmanaged certificate chain structure.
trans-unit.target: Henter mer feilinformasjon fra en ubehandlet sertifikatet kjede struktur.

trans-unit.source: This string is available only on computers with Windows XP Professional or later operating systems.
trans-unit.target: Denne strengen er tilgjengelig bare på datamaskiner med Windows XP Professional eller senere operativsystemer.

trans-unit.source: An empty string ("") is returned if the operating system is not Windows XP Professional or later.
trans-unit.target: En tom streng (""), returneres hvis operativsystemet ikke er Windows XP Professional eller senere.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the <xref uid="langword_csharp_pwszExtendedErrorInfo" name="pwszExtendedErrorInfo" href=""></xref> member of the unmanaged <xref uid="langword_csharp_CERT_CHAIN_ELEMENT" name="CERT_CHAIN_ELEMENT" href=""></xref> structure in the Crypto API.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_pwszExtendedErrorInfo" name="pwszExtendedErrorInfo" href=""> </xref> medlem av den uforvaltede <xref uid="langword_csharp_CERT_CHAIN_ELEMENT" name="CERT_CHAIN_ELEMENT" href=""> </xref> strukturen i kryptering API.
